1
00:00:16,519 --> 00:00:17,760
How much longer do we have to wait?

2
00:00:17,879 --> 00:00:18,679
Yeah.

3
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:20,519
Please be patient.

4
00:00:20,719 --> 00:00:22,320
Physician Yin may be on the way.

5
00:00:22,879 --> 00:00:23,679
Just a moment.

6
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:27,320
Xinyue is late today.

7
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:28,559
She hasn't come yet.

8
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:30,600
I'm thinking

9
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:32,439
maybe something happened.

10
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:37,960
I have some numbers here.

11
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,200
Please take them.

12
00:00:39,520 --> 00:00:41,439
Come for treatment in order tomorrow.

13
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:41,840
Here you are.

14
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:42,960
All right.

15
00:00:44,159 --> 00:00:44,719
Tomorrow?

16
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:48,280
Lady,

17
00:00:48,679 --> 00:00:49,799
my granddaughter has a fever.

18
00:00:50,079 --> 00:00:52,000
She had a seizure twice last night.

19
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:54,280
Can she see the physician first?

20
00:00:55,479 --> 00:00:56,799
I'm sorry I can't help.

21
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,920
You can go to other physicians.

22
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:07,480
Sister Su,

23
00:01:08,439 --> 00:01:09,120
what should we do?

24
00:01:11,239 --> 00:01:12,239
You stay here.

25
00:01:12,599 --> 00:01:13,959
I'll go to Xiao Mansion and ask around.

26
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:30,000
This is not a big deal for me.

27
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,840
Why don't you want to tell me anything?

28
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,560
Does it work?

29
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,639
It can't change anything.

30
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:21,080
You...

31
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,599
But I have a clear conscience.

32
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:32,120
You have no conscience!

33
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:38,520
She needs rest.

34
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:40,039
She needs to recuperate.

35
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:42,680
You're not good at lying.

36
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:48,319
This is a family matter.

37
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,560
I'm just worried about her safety.

38
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,240
Don't worry.

39
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:55,719
If she's safe,

40
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:57,400
I won't interfere.

41
00:02:58,479 --> 00:02:59,159
Now,

42
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,759
the clinic is overcrowded.

43
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:03,280
If Xinyue doesn't show up soon,

44
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,840
the patients will lose faith,

45
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,919
and the clinic won't survive.

46
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:10,280
That can wait.

47
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,159
Yesterday,

48
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:16,360
when Xinyue was making medicine for you,

49
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:20,280
I urged her to leave the Xiao Family.

50
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,000
Do you know

51
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,759
what she said?

52
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:27,439
She said

53
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,479
she wanted to protect the Xiao Family for you.

54
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,879
I thought your relationship

55
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,599
could withstand the storm.

56
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,240
A clinic can be restored,

57
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,639
but a lost love

58
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,319
leaves

59
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,680
a lifelong regret.

60
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:45,520
That's all I have to say.

61
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,879
Please think it over.

62
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,159
Where is Madam Yin?

63
00:04:12,439 --> 00:04:14,319
Didn't she say she would open today?

64
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:17,279
My sister's cough got worse last night.

65
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,279
Yeah.

66
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,199
I'm sorry.

67
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,360
I'm so sorry.

68
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,439
Ms. Yin has some urgent matters at home.

69
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,360
We'll be closed today.

70
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,519
We'll resume as soon as possible.

71
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,240
Please go back first.

72
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,000
If anyone needs help,

73
00:04:30,399 --> 00:04:31,920
you can go to Ren'an Hall for treatment.

74
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,199
How can this be good?

75
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,240
Let's go.

76
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,199
The Women's Clinic has been quite lively lately.

77
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:48,279
Lord Shen, you are truly fortunate.

78
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:50,959
But sometimes, too much attention

79
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,480
might not be

80
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,360
a good thing.

81
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,600
What do you mean by that?

82
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,240
Don't you know

83
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,360
your wife and the Yin Family's daughter

84
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,079
opened the Women's Clinic together?

85
00:05:01,839 --> 00:05:05,800
Moreover, as women, they go out to practice medicine,

86
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,399
and even run a women's clinic.

87
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:10,199
Others may think it's a good deed,

88
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,560
but in reality,

89
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,439
it's just about monopolizing the market

90
00:05:13,439 --> 00:05:14,439
and gathering wealth.

91
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,000
If they don't stop,

92
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,439
the Censors will soon

93
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:21,480
report to the palace

94
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:23,279
that you are indulging your family

95
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,439
in corrupting the social atmosphere.

96
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:29,040
You must be joking.

97
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:33,120
My wife, though from a merchant family,

98
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,839
is well-educated and virtuous,

99
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:37,959
no less than any noble lady.

100
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:41,079
There must be

101
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:43,720
some misunderstanding.

102
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,680
[How did he find me?]

103
00:05:54,879 --> 00:05:56,000
You bitch!

104
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:58,319
I sent a letter to Jiangnan,

105
00:05:58,319 --> 00:05:59,480
why no reply?

106
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,800
So you're hiding in the Changle District!

107
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,519
Let go of me!

108
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:05,959
How are you different from those thugs?

109
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:11,279
You've been gone for a while,

110
00:06:11,639 --> 00:06:12,879
and your audacity has grown.

111
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,040
Running a clinic

112
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,160
disgraces the Shen Family.

113
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,480
If this continues,

114
00:06:17,959 --> 00:06:20,480
you'll ruin my career!

115
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,120
I won't go back.

116
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,600
I want a mutual divorce.

117
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:26,360
What?

118
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:28,160
Mutual divorce?

119
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,600
Do you know what you are saying?

120
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:40,000
I said,

121
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,720
I want to

122
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,480
get a mutual divorce.

123
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,680
If you keep this up,

124
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:51,040
you'll be really out of your depth.

125
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:54,439
Come back with me.

126
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,680
If this continues,

127
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:05,079
something will happen sooner or later.

128
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,399
Shen Yuan won't give up.

129
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:08,879
This clinic

130
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,639
may not be safe.

131
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,680
Let's find a way to get Xin Yue out first.

132
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:17,959
We'll face the difficulties

133
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,680
together.

134
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,279
Your complexion

135
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:39,680
is getting better and better.

136
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:44,079
Thanks to Madam Yin.

137
00:07:44,959 --> 00:07:45,959
But it's a pity

138
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:47,480
Xinyue is in trouble herself,

139
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,959
and may not be able to help you in the future.

140
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:51,399
What's going on?

141
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:52,079
My lady,

142
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,000
to be honest,

143
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,720
Xinyue has had some conflicts

144
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:57,160
with her fiancé recently.

145
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:58,879
She hasn't left her room for days.

146
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:13,120
Why hasn't the door been opened yet?

147
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:13,480
I don't know.

148
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,800
The Minister's wife

149
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,079
seems to be in poor health recently.

150
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,800
She sent someone to ask for a tranquilizer.

151
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,519
You've met her before.

152
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:33,600
You mean

153
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:36,039
if we can find an excuse to treat her,

154
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,279
maybe we can make Mr. Xiao agree.

155
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,759
I didn't say that.

156
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,759
That's what you think.

157
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,039
Thank you for your advice.

158
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,960
You go to the Ministry of Personnel Mansion to deliver the invitation.

159
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,360
I'll go to the Xiao Mansion again.

160
00:08:55,879 --> 00:08:56,080
Okay.

161
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,919
It seems that the Women's Clinic has been very idle recently.

162
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,559
You're right.

163
00:09:05,159 --> 00:09:06,919
The Women's Clinic is indeed cold.

164
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,360
But I came today

165
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:09,919
for another matter.

166
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,279
The wife of the Minister of Revenue

167
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:14,840
was a regular visitor to the Women's Clinic.

168
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:17,600
Recently, her heart disease has been recurring.

169
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,960
and often wakes up from nightmares.

170
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,120
If not treated promptly,

171
00:09:22,679 --> 00:09:23,759
it could cause serious harm.

172
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,360
What does this have to do with me?

173
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:27,759
So she sent someone to invite Xin Yue

174
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:30,399
to treat her specifically.

175
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,960
If you allow her to make a house call...

176
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:32,360
Fine.

177
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:39,120
You just said...

178
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,320
Fine.

179
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:41,080
That's right.

180
00:09:41,919 --> 00:09:43,679
I'm just worried about meeting the Minister of Revenue.

181
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,759
She can recommend me to him.

182
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:49,360
You're just worried about finding a way out.

183
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:50,960
Since you said so,

184
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:51,679
I'm just...

185
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:51,879
Shut up.

186
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:52,600
I'll find a way

187
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:53,480
out.

188
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:55,919
It seems that

189
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:57,919
you took my words to heart.

190
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:01,039
Thank you for your help.

191
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:03,039
Hmm.

192
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:09,879
When will you

193
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:11,000
stop being so quick-witted?

194
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:23,200
You said

195
00:10:24,799 --> 00:10:25,679
Minister of Personnel

196
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,200
is related to Xiao's death.

197
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,759
We've been unable to find new clues.

198
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:32,639
Before my father's death,

199
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:36,120
what did the Minister ask him to investigate?

200
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:39,720
So I want to meet him.

201
00:10:40,519 --> 00:10:41,200
I'll help you.

202
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:43,519
So straightforward?

203
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:46,159
If I don't find out the cause of death,

204
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:48,159
how can I clear my father's name?

205
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,720
The wife of the Minister of Personnel is suspicious

206
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:57,840
and unpredictable.

207
00:10:58,799 --> 00:10:59,600
If I can't cure her,

208
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,679
I'll be regarded as a swindler.

209
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:04,120
The reputation of the Women's Clinic

210
00:11:04,279 --> 00:11:04,960
will be ruined,

211
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:06,200
and I may even lose my life.

212
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:07,399
Aren't you afraid?

213
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:08,080
Of what?

214
00:11:08,679 --> 00:11:10,279
If I were afraid, I wouldn't treat diseases

215
00:11:10,279 --> 00:11:11,000
or save lives.

216
00:11:11,399 --> 00:11:12,480
As a physician,

217
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:14,120
if I just stand by and do nothing

218
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:16,240
because of my own safety,

219
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,480
wouldn't that be putting the cart before the horse?

220
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,320
Besides,

221
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,720
if she dares to harm me,

222
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,120
you can just take me away.

223
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,080
Are you too naive

224
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,919
or do you think too highly of me?

225
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,600
I'm truly naive

226
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,240
and I truly think highly of you.

227
00:11:44,039 --> 00:11:45,840
Watch your words.

228
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:50,679
My Lord,

229
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:51,840
we've found out

230
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,360
the leader of the foreign merchants who traded with Yin Shifeng

231
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,039
is named Suleiman.

232
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:56,120
The Women's clinic has just opened for a while.

233
00:11:56,519 --> 00:11:57,960
My Lord and Madam Yin pretended to be husband and wife

234
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,279
[to rescue Madam Lin at the Bright Moon Pavilion.]

235
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,159
[It's him.]

236
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:16,320
Brother Xiao.

237
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,519
Please take a seat.

238
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,240
Come on.

239
00:12:35,559 --> 00:12:37,320
You're having a good chat, huh?

240
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,120
Stop right there!

241
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,240
Who are you?

242
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,159
Why are you coming out of the Lord's room?

243
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,360
I took a wrong turn.

244
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,440
What's that in your chest?

245
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,360
I told you,

246
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,440
I just went to the wrong room.

247
00:12:51,039 --> 00:12:51,879
Wrong room?

248
00:12:52,919 --> 00:12:54,159
Do you think I'm that easy to fool?

249
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,159
What do you want?

250
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,679
Hand over what you're holding,

251
00:12:59,120 --> 00:12:59,799
or

252
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:01,759
don't blame me for being rude.

253
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:05,879
Brother Xiao, please wait here.

254
00:13:06,039 --> 00:13:06,559
I'll go check.

255
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:08,720
I'll go with you.

256
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:09,720
Let's go.

257
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,919
Hand it over!

258
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:11,879
Now!

259
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:12,240
Stop!

260
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:16,799
Don't be rude!

261
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:18,720
My Lord,

262
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,559
what's going on?

263
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:20,960
I saw him

264
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,320
sneak out of your room.

265
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,120
Did you see it with your own eyes?

266
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:25,559
There's only one room here.

267
00:13:25,799 --> 00:13:27,440
You can't fall from the sky, can you?

268
00:13:28,559 --> 00:13:28,960
Nong,

269
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:30,639
what's going on?

270
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,600
My Lord,

271
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:32,519
I

272
00:13:33,039 --> 00:13:33,720
went to the wrong room.

273
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:34,279
Nonsense!

274
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,360
He's lying!

275
00:13:35,679 --> 00:13:37,039
What's that in your chest?

276
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,159
You must have stolen it from the lord's room.

277
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,240
Mr. Xiao,

278
00:13:44,879 --> 00:13:47,559
I'm willing to cooperate with you

279
00:13:48,159 --> 00:13:51,799
because you're a renowned businessman in Chang'an.

280
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,440
But now it seems

281
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:57,159
you have other intentions towards me.

282
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,639
Brother Su,

283
00:14:00,519 --> 00:14:01,679
do you mean you don't trust me?

284
00:14:02,519 --> 00:14:03,399
Mr. Xiao,

285
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:04,960
you're mistaken.

286
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,600
What are you talking about?

287
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:09,919
If you treat me with sincerity,

288
00:14:10,399 --> 00:14:13,080
I will definitely repay you with the same.

289
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,000
Ask your brother

290
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:17,080
to take out the letter from his chest.

291
00:14:17,559 --> 00:14:18,600
Let's take a look.

292
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,279
Then we'll know.

293
00:14:22,559 --> 00:14:24,879
You're very cautious,

294
00:14:25,879 --> 00:14:27,320
and not afraid of hurting the harmony.

295
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,480
Mr. Xiao,

296
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,159
if you are unwilling

297
00:14:32,519 --> 00:14:33,840
to cooperate

298
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,559
in such a trivial matter,

299
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:40,879
how can I feel at ease working with you?

300
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:45,360
I didn't expect that in your eyes,

301
00:14:46,879 --> 00:14:49,159
the Xiao Family is so insignificant.

302
00:14:54,919 --> 00:14:55,480
Nong?
